by stof at 2015-05-22T14:17:14Z

:+1: The default value cannot be changed in DoctrineBundle because it would be a BC break for existing projects, but the underscore is a much saner choice than the default naming strategy keeping camel-cased names. It has much less compatibility issues across platforms.
